Lastly, the left-align
content can start to feel

43
00:02:12,330 --> 00:02:16,180
unbalanced leaving large empty
areas on the right of the screen.

44
00:02:16,180 --> 00:02:19,060
Choosing break points based
on content requirements

45
00:02:19,060 --> 00:02:23,580
is more future proof than basing
them on a specific set of devices.

46
00:02:23,580 --> 00:02:26,255
You'll know those requirements
will be satisfied no matter

47
00:02:26,255 --> 00:02:27,745
what devices get thrown your way.

